  "abstract": "ICRISAT is surging ahead with its innovations, which are described\r\nin detail in this publication. It is in fact creating a legacy of\r\ninnovations. Egged on by its dynamic leadership, its budding\r\nscientists have always displayed a keen sense of awareness of\r\nthe changing context of agricultural research with its inherent\r\ncomplexities, and have risen to the occasion to become\r\nchampions of the poor.",
